{"tid":1308641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"只要仲有150同iang，真普選都冇用","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:59:26.000Z","uid":173326,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff3462ce72793286b46bff180b5f7025b8ba97f","tid":1308641,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"因為而家幼稚園班蝗仔係唔識廣東話，相信小學為提高收生會實行蝗語教育。當佢地去到中學嘅時候，家長就會要求母語教育，所謂母語係蝗語，因為到時候蝗仔會多過本地人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中學以前有大陸人插班但佢地會學廣東話作為母語。畢業唔夠6年，有時經過學校會聽到啲高年級已經大聲講緊蝗語。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我完全冇想像過蝗仔嘅入侵速度係咁快，就算香港有真普選，只會越來越多市民支持建制派，因為越來越多蝗仔大個有投票權，甚至加入藍絲支持政府。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港下屆立法會選舉相信會見到呢個現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果想香港繼續係香港人嘅香港，取消150、iang係必須</span></span><br />\n<br />\niang詳情：<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/visas/IANG.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2Fvisas%2FIANG.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ga%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=15ae929e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/visas/IANG.html</a>"},{"pid":"61f7d2b4f01ec4a9ac9bcf93e00ad4badc87f25a","tid":1308641,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:52:25.000Z","msg":"有時間可唔可以去維基百科寫一寫IANG的爭議和影響。<br />\n記得維基寫嘢一定要有sources (例如係報紙)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9D%9E%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E7%95%99%E6%B8%AF%E2%95%B1%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E2%2595%25B1%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25